%% MbengkelIn — Entity Relationship Diagram
%% Generated from the live Supabase project (ref: nerrnpbopdfrdcfvjowx)
%% Scope: public schema + auth.users (the auth-schema anchor public.users extends).
%% Note: auth.* internal tables (sessions, identities, refresh_tokens, mfa_*, etc.)
%%       are omitted; only auth.users is shown since it is the only auth entity the
%%       app's public schema references.
%% Convention-only links (NOT enforced FK constraints): bengkels.provider_uid,
%%       vehicles.customer_id — drawn here because they relate logically.
%% Rendered in pure black & white (no fill colors) via the init theme directive below.

